com.inrix.sdk

Class GasStationManager.GasStationsOnRouteOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.GasStationManager.GasStationsOnRouteOptions
  • Enclosing class:
    GasStationManager

    public static final class GasStationManager.GasStationsOnRouteOptions
extends Object
    Contains options for requesting gas stations along a route. Default radius is GasStationManager.GasStationsOnRouteOptions.DEFAULT_RADIUS_IN_MILES miles. Default distance is GasStationManager.GasStationsOnRouteOptions.DEFAULT_DISTANCE_IN_MILES miles.
    See Also:
    GasStationManager.getGasStationsOnRoute(GasStationsOnRouteOptions, IGasStationsResponseListener).

        public void setRadius(double radius)
        Set the radius distance to find gas stations on a route.
        Parameters:
        radius - The distance in selected units (see UserPreferences.Unit), either miles or meters.
        Throws:
        GasStationManager.GasStationManagerException - when: radius is equal or less than GasStationManager.GasStationsOnRouteOptions.MIN_RADIUS_IN_MILES and bigger than GasStationManager.GasStationsOnRouteOptions.MAX_RADIUS_IN_MILES miles.
